            <h2>Description of Service</h2>
            <p>My Japanese Name Translator provides a <strong>free online tool</strong> for converting English names into Japanese writing systems, including Katakana, Hiragana, Kanji (ateji), and Romaji. The service is provided at no cost to users.</p>
            <p>The Website is currently <strong>ad-free</strong>. In the future, we may implement display advertising (such as Google AdSense) to support the continued free operation of the service. Any changes to the service model will be reflected in an update to these Terms.</p>

