            <h2>Name Translation Accuracy Disclaimer</h2>
            <p>Our Japanese name translation tool uses phonetic transliteration algorithms and a curated name database to convert English names into Japanese scripts. While we strive for accuracy, please understand the following:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Translations are <strong>phonetic approximations</strong> — Japanese phonetics differ from English, and some sounds do not have direct equivalents</li>
                <li>Kanji translations use <strong>ateji</strong> (characters selected for sound rather than meaning) and may not carry the same significance as native Japanese names</li>
                <li>There may be <strong>multiple valid translations</strong> for a single English name, and our tool presents one interpretation</li>
                <li>Translations should <strong>not be used as the sole basis</strong> for permanent applications (such as tattoos or legal documents) without independent verification from a native Japanese speaker or qualified linguist</li>
                <li>We do not guarantee that translations will be identical to official or standardized versions used by Japanese institutions</li>
            </ul>

